    "causal_summary": "Adds a read-only getGraphReadinessSnapshot() helper to ensure-ready.ts and wires it into code_graph_status so readiness.action surfaces full_scan / selective_reindex / none instead of always emitting 'none'. Closes the 4-hour staleness drift observability gap from 010 findings §3 without lowering DEFAULT_DEBOUNCE_MS=2000 (research §5.3 explicitly rejects that as the first fix). Preserves the existing top-level freshness field shape on status responses. Side-effect freedom verified by mock-surface assertions on the write-side code-graph-db exports and on ensureCodeGraphReady.",
